## Summary

**Created second project agent `clarvis-db`**, seeded brain, implemented retrieval benchmarking, verified multi-agent aggregation.

What was done:
- **Created agent**: `project_agent.py create clarvis-db --repo GranusClarvis/clarvis-db.git --branch main` → cloned to `/home/agent/agents/clarvis-db/`, lite brain initialized (5 collections)
- **Wrote golden QA**: 12 repo-specific Q/A pairs covering install, test, build, Hebbian/STDP engines, VectorStore API, project structure
- **Seeded brain**: 12 memories seeded, retrieval verified (P@1=0.833, P@3=1.0, MRR=0.903 via project_agent.py; P@1=0.75, P@3=0.833, MRR=0.829 via orchestration_benchmark.py)
